SynchronizedMultipleInstanceFlow
public class StaticPartialJoinMultipleInstancesFlow
extends PredefinedStructuredFlow
implements StaticPartialJoinMultipleInstancesFlow

Meets the Static Partial Join for Multiple Instances pattern (WFP34) if acceptValue > 1 and acceptValue < nInstances. If nInstances = acceptValue is equivalent to the SynchronizedMultipleInstanceFlow.

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
